---
title: Call to action
metadesc: Call to action styling
typography: true
intro: |-
  Calls to action are an integral part the user experience. As calls to action should always include a user action, they should either be used with a `button` or an `a`. All CTAs can include an icon with the class `.icon` either to the left or the right of the text. If an icon is included, you need to include either the `.cta--left-icon` or `.cta--right-icon` classes, respectively, to ensure the icon is spaced, sized, and styled correctly.
---

{% from 'icon.njk' import icon %}

